 dispbuffer - what wayland displays
 decor - decorations
 frame - what you see inside the displayed-buffer  Ch 26
   parameters, keep:
     name left top height width (in pixels) minibuffer font
     foreground-color background-color mouse-color cursor-color
     internal-border-width unsplittable visibility 
   parameters, toss:
     auto-raise auto-lower vertical-scroll-bars horizontal-scroll-bars
     icon-type border color cursor-type border-width parent-id
 window - display of text buffer
   NEW - text voids (per-line region of blank space -- for diagrams and
         equations )
 modeline -
|#

